00:11:00.127 --> 00:11:02.663 position:13% line:83% align:start
[TSUJI] Yeah, it's a thing.
Headmistress' policy.

00:11:02.796 --> 00:11:04.533 position:27% line:83% align:start
Eimei has ranked
in the top five academies

00:11:04.665 --> 00:11:08.002 position:7% line:83% align:start
