it's really competitive.

00:11:08.135 --> 00:11:10.070 position:27% line:83% align:start
But the students
like the games too.

00:11:10.204 --> 00:11:13.307 position:5% line:83% align:start
More importantly, snack shopping
at lunch gets crazy!

00:11:13.440 --> 00:11:14.909 position:30% line:89% align:start
So, if you want

00:11:15.042 --> 00:11:16.076 position:19% line:83% align:start
any chance of snagging
the popular chocolate cornet.

00:11:16.210 --> 00:11:17.579 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHIRAYUKI]
Please forgive

00:11:17.711 --> 00:11:19.113 position:13% line:83% align:start
the untimely interruption,
Master.

00:11:19.648 --> 00:11:22.082 position:7% line:83% align:start
We've received a very favorable
game request.

00:11:22.216 --> 00:11:24.885 position:21% line:83% align:start
The challenger's name
is Haru Urasaka.

00:11:25.019 --> 00:11:27.721 position:13% line:83% align:start
She's a third-year student
from District Eleven.

00:11:29.490 --> 00:11:32.426 position:30% line:83% align:start
Man. Looks like
life's about to get real busy

00:11:32.561 --> 00:11:33.894 position:27% line:89% align:start
from here on out.

00:11:35.963 --> 00:11:38.832 position:30% line:83% align:start
Alright, folks!
The wait is meow over!

00:11:38.966 --> 00:11:42.036 position:5% line:83% align:start
Today's highly anticipated event
is about to begin!

00:11:42.169 --> 00:11:45.640 position:35% line:83% align:start
But first,
meow about I introduce myself?

00:11:46.173 --> 00:11:48.242 position:30% line:83% align:start
Coming straight
meowta Ouka Academy,

00:11:48.375 --> 00:11:51.845 position:10% line:83% align:start
repping Libra, I'm your host,
second-year Suzuran Kazami!

00:11:51.979 --> 00:11:53.447 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHIRAYUKI]
Libra's the Island media group

00:11:53.582 --> 00:11:54.949 position:16% line:89% align:start
behind the news app LNN.

00:11:55.082 --> 00:11:57.451 position:27% line:83% align:start
They also manage
the streaming platform ITube.

00:11:57.586 --> 00:11:58.886 position:24% line:89% align:start
And are responsible

00:11:59.019 --> 00:12:00.421 position:33% line:83% align:start
for arranging
high-profile game events.

00:12:00.555 --> 00:12:03.924 position:24% line:83% align:start
[SUZURAN] First up,
our challenger, Haru Urasaka!

00:12:04.058 --> 00:12:05.426 position:24% line:89% align:start
Ranked Three Stars,

00:12:05.560 --> 00:12:07.596 position:7% line:83% align:start
her hobbies include road trips
and Visual Kei!

00:12:07.728 --> 00:12:08.563 position:44% line:89% align:start
'Sup?

00:12:08.697 --> 00:12:09.964 position:35% line:89% align:start
[cheering]

00:12:10.097 --> 00:12:11.465 position:24% line:83% align:start
And the one meeting
her challenge

00:12:11.600 --> 00:12:13.000 position:10% line:89% align:start
