00:12:15.503 --> 00:12:17.071 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Who's she even talking about?

00:12:17.204 --> 00:12:18.939 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SUZURAN] You all know him
as the fastest ever

00:12:19.073 --> 00:12:20.441 position:21% line:89% align:start
