00:13:47.428 --> 00:13:50.699 position:50% line:89% align:start
âª

00:13:50.831 --> 00:13:52.132 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SUZURAN]
Woah!

00:13:52.266 --> 00:13:54.034 position:24% line:83% align:start
She's bringing out
the big guns this time!

00:13:54.168 --> 00:13:56.136 position:27% line:83% align:start
No bike like this
has ever been recorded

00:13:56.270 --> 00:13:57.838 position:10% line:89% align:start
