00:13:57.971 --> 00:13:59.507 position:24% line:83% align:start
[SARASA] Definitely
Urasaka's secret weapon.

00:13:59.641 --> 00:14:02.510 position:7% line:83% align:start
After all, vehicle performance
is the key to this game.

00:14:02.644 --> 00:14:05.145 position:7% line:83% align:start
