00:14:06.715 --> 00:14:08.817 position:7% line:83% align:start
Any sensible player would look
to abilities

00:14:08.949 --> 00:14:10.819 position:13% line:89% align:start
that focus on obstruction.

00:14:10.951 --> 00:14:13.320 position:5% line:89% align:start
Whatever vehicle Shinohara uses.

00:14:13.954 --> 00:14:15.022 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:14:15.155 --> 00:14:16.591 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SUZURAN]
Shinohara!

00:14:16.725 --> 00:14:19.093 position:10% line:83% align:start
Are you seriously gonna race
a motorcycle on foot?

00:14:19.226 --> 00:14:20.961 position:30% line:83% align:start
