00:14:22.996 --> 00:14:24.766 position:16% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO] My heart's gonna
explode for sure!

00:14:24.898 --> 00:14:27.502 position:13% line:83% align:start
[SHIRAYUKI] Our data shows
Urasaka's main ability

00:14:27.635 --> 00:14:28.936 position:16% line:89% align:start
is "remove speed limit."

00:14:29.069 --> 00:14:30.170 position:7% line:89% align:start
The effect of which allows her

00:14:30.304 --> 00:14:31.972 position:38% line:83% align:start
to exceed
her vehicle's top speed.

00:14:32.106 --> 00:14:34.576 position:27% line:83% align:start
Augmenting this,
is her second ability,

00:14:34.709 --> 00:14:35.943 position:30% line:89% align:start
"Acceleration".

00:14:36.076 --> 00:14:37.444 position:27% line:83% align:start
Third in sequence
is "Safety Device",

00:14:37.579 --> 00:14:40.481 position:16% line:83% align:start
an ability that protects
both user and systems.

00:14:40.948 --> 00:14:42.149 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
If this goes as expected,

00:14:42.282 --> 00:14:43.984 position:33% line:83% align:start
she won't use
her defensive ability,

00:14:44.118 --> 00:14:45.820 position:24% line:83% align:start
so my interference
shouldn't be blocked.

00:14:45.986 --> 00:14:47.388 position:38% line:83% align:start
[URASAKA]
It's too late to change 'em now,

00:14:47.522 --> 00:14:49.323 position:19% line:83% align:start
so there's no real harm
in telling you.

00:14:49.758 --> 00:14:52.192 position:21% line:83% align:start
I'm using the Nullify
Interference ability.

00:14:52.326 --> 00:14:54.094 position:16% line:83% align:start
It's a defensive utility
that cancels out

00:14:54.228 --> 00:14:56.330 position:16% line:83% align:start
your opponent's attempts
to impede you.

00:14:56.463 --> 00:14:58.065 position:21% line:83% align:start
I bet that you picked
obstructive abilities

00:14:58.198 --> 00:14:59.734 position:33% line:83% align:start
in all three
of your active slots,

00:14:59.868 --> 00:15:01.201 position:35% line:89% align:start
didn't you?

00:15:01.335 --> 00:15:03.337 position:19% line:83% align:start
That's really too bad.
They're worthless now.

00:15:03.470 --> 00:15:04.438 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

00:15:04.572 --> 00:15:07.241 position:19% line:83% align:start
Let's get this moving,
Speed Girl.

00:15:07.374 --> 00:15:08.442 position:41% line:89% align:start
[humph]

00:15:08.877 --> 00:15:11.945 position:13% line:83% align:start
Here we go! We've kept you
in suspense long enough!

00:15:12.079 --> 00:15:13.280 position:38% line:83% align:start
[SUZURAN]
Meow'all ready for this?

00:15:13.414 --> 00:15:15.349 position:30% line:83% align:start
Who will reach
the finish line first?

00:15:15.482 --> 00:15:18.318 position:33% line:83% align:start
Don't blink!
It'll be over in an instant!

00:15:18.952 --> 00:15:21.790 position:27% line:89% align:start
Three. Two. One.

00:15:21.922 --> 00:15:22.891 position:44% line:89% align:start
Boom!

00:15:23.023 --> 00:15:24.992 position:38% line:89% align:start
[whoosh]

00:15:27.729 --> 00:15:29.463 position:41% line:89% align:start
[gasps]

