[thud]

00:15:45.847 --> 00:15:47.214 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Seriously, people.

00:15:47.347 --> 00:15:48.883 position:21% line:89% align:start
Give me some credit.

00:15:49.016 --> 00:15:51.820 position:7% line:83% align:start
You think a Seven Star like me
