00:15:57.291 --> 00:15:58.459 position:38% line:83% align:start
[HIROTO]
Huh?

00:15:58.593 --> 00:16:00.260 position:35% line:83% align:start
[SHIRAYUKI]
It's an assist ability

00:16:00.394 --> 00:16:01.930 position:16% line:83% align:start
that temporarily disables
your opponent's defenses.

00:16:02.062 --> 00:16:04.231 position:33% line:83% align:start
